,"uid":198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:08:09.000Z","msg":"去過，我係波斯尼亞入去<br />\n沒咩特別，唔洗太驚<br />\n<br />\n利申 渣bno<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2w1120.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2w1120.jpg&h=b7935d36&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/190718_67ed0120526bf85d41a8c29dac0a0f84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F190718_67ed0120526bf85d41a8c29dac0a0f84.jpg&h=a8741a3b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y38183.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY38183.jpg&h=0d2007bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/190728_26bdb15e12f1d0386f8111cf82fe25e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F190728_26bdb15e12f1d0386f8111cf82fe25e7.jpg&h=37af27a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0864fd248592a8145efb305d2a229a909db200ea","tid":4590,"uid":198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:09:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用BNO<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇分別，你一比人印左就返唔到塞爾維亞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會，我試過，沒問題，個別痴線佬，會一野用原子筆刪左你個名，再補serbia個印，但一定入到境"},{"pid":"bcb0cb511e74f71df0b7d3ffb2d5cc732ca26559","tid":4590,"uid":198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:10:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用BNO<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇分別，你一比人印左就返唔到塞爾維亞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會，我試過，沒問題，個別痴線佬，會一野用原子筆刪左你個科索沃印，再補serbia個印，但一定入到境</blockquote>"},{"pid":"736cae9b98fd01fc900b439adc763407154ff226","tid":4590,"uid":13353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:12:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用BNO<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇分別，你一比人印左就返唔到塞爾維亞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會，我試過，沒問題，個別痴線佬，會一野用原子筆刪左你個科索沃印，再補serbia個印，但一定入到境</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上次我見住同行個澳洲妹因為馬其頓入，有印，係科塞邊境比海關趕返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9f761e834e96b5618655e63c27c5b3322326cd","tid":4590,"uid":26045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T17:15:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用BNO<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇分別，你一比人印左就返唔到塞爾維亞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會，我試過，沒問題，個別痴線佬，會一野用原子筆刪左你個名，再補serbia個印，但一定入到境</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我出入都係經塞爾維亞，科索沃海關有蓋印，返去都冇事<br />\n塞爾維亞都準備好認低威承認科索沃，佢關員開始唔玩野，不過科索沃入面嗰班塞族分離分子就好難講"},{"pid":"5108976aba1113145caa00e3bc94afcaeb989f9d","tid":4590,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T01:11:48.000Z","msg":"係咪要係歐洲主要城市轉機過去"},{"pid":"9dec84c1ec65b9c77d3a0f6eff2c7ffe78a5dba6","tid":4590,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T02:21:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪要係歐洲主要城市轉機過去</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4078d8831a581f2f6148fdee1317bac05ecba1a0","tid":4590,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:54:53.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"a062ac6bb07eb7d0a34b6e3aea6bfd6e32a3863a","tid":4590,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:56:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪要係歐洲主要城市轉機過去</blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d280dd8b2dc23c7ceb281f2acfe3c74359d67f68","tid":4590,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T03:59:59.000Z","msg":"巴絲們可否講下點解你地會去呢度？<br />\n有咩吸引之處？<br />\n<